{
  "stem": "422.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For being interrogated, and it shouldn't come out that we're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we had no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All of a sudden, the German woman, on the order of the police, of the gestapo, gives us a separate room, with a clean bed, a warm blanket.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were pinching each other, if it's true.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "From Auschwitz right in a bed, and brings us-- and gives us-- calls us in for warm soup with bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I said, this must be a dream.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We're dreaming.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's not true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But still, we couldn't close our eyes from excitement, and we couldn't-- from worrying what's going to happen in the-- in the morning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But God helped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "During the night, we hear all the sirens in that little-- in that town, blowing away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the radio announces-- I understand German-- announces that the Russian army is very near.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We are surrounded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the whole-- the whole town is being evacuated because it was an industrial town, doing-- with a lot of factories.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Every factory, every bridge will be blown up by the SS.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It will be dynamite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They don't leave for the Russians a thing that can be useful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the whole population got to come to the-- you know, to the trains, where the train is going away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we'd be shipped-- we'd be shipped to deep Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I say to her, what shall we do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shall we hide?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we might be-- after being almost on the way of getting-- being free, people, if you hide, you might be blown up by the SS.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They warned people not to hide, because everything will be blown up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not to stay back, but go with the transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
